=== Setsusha ===
The following shrines are enshrined as shrines within the precincts and shrines outside the precincts.
*Suesha
** Ebisu Shrine - Deities enshrined: Kanayamahiko no Mikoto, Kanayamahime no Mikoto, Toyoukehime no Mikoto, Kotosushi no Mikoto
** Haredo Shrine - Deities enshrined: Ibukito no Mikoto, Seoritsu Hime no Mikoto, Hasakai Tsu Hime no Mikoto, Hasasa Sura Hime no Mikoto
** Kotaisha - Deities enshrined: Isanaki no Mikoto, Isanami no Mikoto, Amaterasu Omikami
** Kusunosha Shrine - Deities enshrined: Owatatsumi no Mikoto, Ichikishimahimekami
* Otabisho
** Kusunoki Shrine - Enshrined deity: Owatatsumi no Mikoto, Ichikishimahime no Kami
* Others
** Fudosha
