=== Festival ===
The following festivals are held at Tarumi Shrine each year.
* Monthly Festival/Monthly Festival (1st and 15th of every month)
* Fudosha Goma (8th of every month)
* Saitan Festival (January 1st)
* Tarumi Ebisu (January 10th)
* Donto Festival (January 15th)
*Setsubun Festival (February 3rd)
* Yoimiya (Otabisho Festival) (May 20th)
* Spring Festival (May 21st)
* Summer Purification (June 30th)
* Yoimiya (Otabisho Festival) (October 20th)
* Autumn Festival (October 21st) - ``Regular Festival''.
* Great Purification (December 31st)

